# Layout Module Specific Standards

> **Related Rules**: See [Architecture Standards](./architecture.mdc), [Accessibility Standards](./accessibility.mdc), [Theming](./theming.mdc)

## Responsive Design

- Support multiple screen sizes
- Use responsive breakpoints
- Test on different devices
- Mobile-first approach

## Layout State Management

- Use Signals for layout state
- Manage sidebar collapse/expand
- Handle navigation state
- Theme switching support

## Navigation Structure

- Clear navigation hierarchy
- Keyboard navigation support (see [Accessibility](./accessibility.mdc))
- Breadcrumb navigation
- Active route highlighting

